  "id": "api/index/const/asapScheduler",
  "title": "asapScheduler",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"page-actions\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/edit/master/src/internal/scheduler/asap.ts?message=docs(index)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L55-L54\" aria-label=\"编辑建议\" title=\"编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/tree/7.5.2/src/internal/scheduler/asap.ts#L55-L54\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n  </div>\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/index\", \"name\": \"rxjs/index\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/index/const/asapScheduler\", \"name\": \"asapScheduler\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/index\">rxjs/index</a>\n    </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"asapscheduler\">asapScheduler<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/const/asapScheduler#asapscheduler\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">稳定</label>\n    \n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  \n\n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-result=\"on\">越快越好（as soon as possible）调度器</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Asap Scheduler</p>\n\n<p></p>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const <a href=\"api/index/const/asapScheduler\" class=\"code-anchor\">asapScheduler</a>: AsapScheduler;\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/const/asapScheduler#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\"><span class=\"informal\">尽可能快地执行任务，因为它可以异步执行</span></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><span class=\"informal\">Perform task as fast as it can be performed asynchronously</span></p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">当你使用 <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> 调度器来延迟任务时，它的行为与 <a href=\"api/index/const/asyncScheduler\"><code>asyncScheduler</code></a> 调度器相同。但是，如果你将延迟设置为 <code>0</code>，则 <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> 将等待当前同步执行的代码结束，然后尝试尽快执行给定的任务。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> scheduler behaves the same as <a href=\"api/index/const/asyncScheduler\"><code>asyncScheduler</code></a> scheduler when you use it to delay task\nin time. If however you set delay to <code>0</code>, <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> will wait for current synchronously executing\ncode to end and then it will try to execute given task as fast as possible.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> 调度器将尽最大努力减少当前执行代码结束和计划任务开始之间的时间。这使它成为执行所谓“延迟”的最佳候选者。传统上，这是通过调用 <code>setTimeout(deferredTask, 0)</code> 来实现的，但是该技术会引入一些不必要的延迟（尽管很小）。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> scheduler will do its best to minimize time between end of currently executing code\nand start of scheduled task. This makes it best candidate for performing so called \"deferring\".\nTraditionally this was achieved by calling <code>setTimeout(deferredTask, 0)</code>, but that technique involves\nsome (although minimal) unwanted delay.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">请注意，使用 <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> 调度器并不一定意味着你的任务将在当前执行代码之后首先处理。特别是，如果之前还用 <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> 安排了某个任务，则那个任务将首先执行。话虽如此，如果你需要异步调度任务，而且希望越快越好，那么 <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> scheduler 会是你最好的选择。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Note that using <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> scheduler does not necessarily mean that your task will be first to process\nafter currently executing code. In particular, if some task was also scheduled with <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> before,\nthat task will execute first. That being said, if you need to schedule task asynchronously, but\nas soon as possible, <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> scheduler is your best bet.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"example\" translation-result=\"on\">例子<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/const/asapScheduler#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"example\">Example<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/const/asapScheduler#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">比较异步和越快越好调度器&#x3C;</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Compare async and asap scheduler&#x3C;</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\nimport { <a href=\"api/index/const/asapScheduler\" class=\"code-anchor\">asapScheduler</a>, <a href=\"api/index/const/asyncScheduler\" class=\"code-anchor\">asyncScheduler</a> } <a href=\"api/index/function/from\" class=\"code-anchor\">from</a> 'rxjs';\n\nasyncScheduler.schedule(() => console.log('async')); // scheduling 'async' first...\nasapScheduler.schedule(() => console.log('<a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a>'));\n\n// Logs:\n// \"<a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a>\"\n// \"async\"\n// ... but '<a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a>' goes <a href=\"api/index/function/first\" class=\"code-anchor\">first</a>!\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/deprecations\n - api/index\n - api/index/const/asap\n - api/index/const/asyncScheduler\n - api/index/function/generate\n - guide/scheduler\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/index\n - api/index/const/asap\n - api/index/const/asapScheduler#asapscheduler\n - api/index/const/asapScheduler#description\n - api/index/const/asapScheduler#example\n - api/index/const/asyncScheduler\n - api/index/function/first\n - api/index/function/from\n - https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/edit/master/src/internal/scheduler/asap.ts?message=docs(index)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L55-L54\n - https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/tree/7.5.2/src/internal/scheduler/asap.ts#L55-L54\n-->"
